    <a href="tel:+13238704790" class="branch"><b>West Hollywood</b><span>(323) 870-4790</span></a>
    <a href="tel:+14243250520" class="branch"><b>Los Angeles</b><span>(424) 325-0520</span></a>
    <a href="tel:+14242080228" class="branch"><b>Thousand Oaks</b><span>(424) 208-0228</span></a>
    <a href="tel:+16263764458" class="branch"><b>Pasadena</b><span>(626) 376-4458</span></a>
    <a href="tel:+12134019019" class="branch"><b>Irvine</b><span>(213) 401-9019</span></a>
  </div></aside></div></div></section>

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>CSLB #1138898 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>What Sharp microwave repair costs in LA</h2>
    <table class="price-table">
      <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Waived with repair</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Magnetron</td><td>$220 – $360</td><td>5-7 year fatigue</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Drawer linear actuator</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>Slide-in/out motor; 7-10 yr</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Roller guide / slide rail</td><td>$140 – $220</td><td>Clean + realign; often no part</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door switch / interlock</td><td>$120 – $200</td><td>Drawer + countertop both</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Control / inverter board</td><td>$280 – $460</td><td>Inverter = distinct architecture</td></tr>
      <tr><td>SuperSteam reservoir sensor</td><td>$160 – $260</td><td>SSC-series combi</td></tr>
      <tr><td>SuperSteam descale service</td><td>$120 – $180</td><td>Hard-water LA zones</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/sharp/">Sharp brand hub</a> · <a href="/brands/wolf-microwave-repair/">Wolf microwave (Sharp drawer OEM)</a> · <a href="/brands/thermador-microwave-repair/">Thermador microwave (Sharp drawer OEM)</a> · <a href="/brands/miele-microwave-repair/">Miele microwave (Sharp drawer OEM)</a> · <a href="/brands/panasonic-microwave-repair/">Panasonic microwave (Inverter countertop peer)</a> · <a href="/services/microwave-repair/">Microwave repair (service hub)</a> · <a href="/price-list/microwave-repair-cost/">Microwave repair cost</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Drawer microwave — the Sharp licensing ecosystem</h2>
    <p>Sharp invented the drawer microwave in 1999 with the Insight Microwave Drawer and has licensed the chassis to three luxury brands continuously since. Each brand sells the drawer under its own nameplate with proprietary front-fascia trim and brand-specific firmware, but the magnetron, linear actuator, roller guide, controller board, and door-interlock architecture underneath are all Sharp. Practical implication for LA service: our Sharp drawer parts stock and drawer-mechanism repair experience applies across the full Sharp + Wolf + Thermador + Miele drawer footprint. If you have a luxury drawer microwave in a custom-built kitchen, there's a high chance Sharp built it.</p>
    <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:14px 0;">
      <li style="padding:6px 0;"><b>Sharp SMD2470A / SMD3070A / SKS-series</b> — OEM reference, direct Sharp nameplate, most accessible pricing tier</li>
      <li style="padding:6px 0;"><b>Wolf ICBMODR / ICBMOTR (Sub-Zero Group)</b> — see <a href="/brands/wolf-microwave-repair/">Wolf microwave</a></li>
      <li style="padding:6px 0;"><b>Thermador MD24WSS / MD30WSS (BSH Irvine parts chain)</b> — see <a href="/brands/thermador-microwave-repair/">Thermador microwave</a></li>
      <li style="padding:6px 0;"><b>Miele EDT-series (Gütersloh Germany firmware + trim)</b> — see <a href="/brands/miele-microwave-repair/">Miele microwave</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Sharp microwave repair — frequently asked</h2>
    {faqs.map(f => (<details class="faq"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p set:html={f.a}></p></details>))}
